               <p>Before Mr. Justice Bayley.</p>
               <p>18. 
               
                  <persName id="t18231203-18-defend215" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     HENNESSY
                  <interp inst="t18231203-18-defend215" type="surname" value="HENNESSY"></interp>
